title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - Aircraft & Avionics Update 2 - new beta available
description:
In this video we will go through the changes in the second beta build of Aircraft & Avionics Update (AAU) 2 which has been released a few days ago. The second build contains several fixes for issues reported by simmers but in addition to this it will also bring a lot of new functionality especially to both Boeings.
